	user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	username VARCHAR(50),
	email VARCHAR(100),
	feedback_preference BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   username VARCHAR(50),
   email VARCHAR(100),
   feedback_preference BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE feedback_preferences (
   user_id INT,
   like_feedback BOOLEAN,
   dislike_feedback BOOLEAN,
   PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
)

CREATE TABLE user_input_log (
   log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   user_id INT,
   input_text TEXT,
   input_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  date_joined TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE feedback_preferences (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  receive_email_notification BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
  receive_sms_notification BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
  receive_app_notification BOOLEAN NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE user_input_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  input_text TEXT NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE user_interaction_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  action_taken VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    last_login TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE profile_updates (
    update_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    update_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    update_value TEXT,
    update_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);
